            "body": "`vim.lsp.diagnostic.on_publish_diagnostics` passes `params.diagnostics` through `tbl_map (keeps order)` into `vim.diagnostic.set`, and `get()` returns them as stored. the only reorder is table.sort in `toqflist`. \r\n\r\n> it does not look like there is much demand for https://github.com/neovim/neovim/issues/20499 ...\r\n\r\nYes, this issue has been around for quite a while and hasn’t gotten much attention. So I’ll leave it to you. Also, opts.sort actually appears in many places.",
